[LABEL Давай братан!][VIDEO gops1_gop1_speaking_soft.mp4][AUDIO silent_1][BGNDVIDEO gops1_gop1_idle_soft.mp4][TIMEEXPIRED mark_final9][ANSWERTIME 20]
